    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Preparing a clay object for firing by trimming away seams and other blemishes with a metal tool; especially used upon clay objects formed with molds.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
